    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses intense feelings of failure and guilt, suggesting that their children would be better off if they were no longer around. The assistant consistently responds with empathy, refutes the user's logic regarding self-harm as a \"gift,\" and repeatedly urges the user to seek professional help or contact a crisis line.",
